CatDescriptText: Banner hanging on railing reads "Headquarters: of the Annual Convention of Grand Lodge State of Pennsylvania of Pythias of N.A. S.A. E. A. A. L. A. July 24-25-26-27th Charles W. Brown Grand Chancellor
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of men and women, some wearing ceremonial necklaces, some wearing ribbon pins, standing on steps and landing of stone building with street number 2522, and banner hanging over railing on porch inscribed "Headquarters: of the Annual Convention of Grand Lodge..."
